Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:02.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started with the Sacred Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting and searching\nfor our dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:06.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a strong bond\nis formed between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:07.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bright future begins now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a secret from Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm back in the modern era and\NI'll be able to relax for a change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:14.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least, that's what I thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My classmates Eri, Yuka and\NAyumi start pestering me about{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:19.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}meeting Inuyasha and\ncreate a fine mess!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:21.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final shard guides us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:22.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other side of the well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new day awaits in\nthe age of warring states!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:26.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:06.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay. Take your time over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll be doing some\nrecuperating, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those rats chewed them up\npretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Use the medicine.\NI'll bring more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:15.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:17.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind. We'll be seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:22.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:38.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:40.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So my sister is still\nin this {\i1}world....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't seem very surprised, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:55.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A little while ago, two girls\nwho seemed like {\i1}shikigami{\i0} appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and took dirt from my sister's shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:07.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That dirt was probably used to\nheal wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which were inflicted on her\nby Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know how you feel about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I'm glad that Kikyo\nwas saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:21.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the one who saved Kikyo from being\neaten away by Naraku's miasma
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0} Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This feels so {\i1}good....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buyo, you're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder how Inuyasha\nis {\i1}doing....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I came back without telling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:50.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo seemed to have regained\nher spiritual powers and looked {\i1}well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but she disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:06.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe Inuyasha really wanted\nto go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even on the way back to\NOld Kaede's village,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it felt awkward speaking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:35.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess I'm second fiddle to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? Why'd you let Kagome\ngo back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't have to ask you permission\nfor everything, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:53.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Weren't you telling Kaede\nabout Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She couldn't interrupt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome was being considerate\nof you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}wasn't....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:06.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't telling her anything\nthat I didn't want overheard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you blame me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....!{\i0} Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:12.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:13.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good {\i1}try....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I guess it only works\nwhen Kagome says it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Of course, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:21.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a second, I thought\nit would work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:26.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Geez! At this rate,\nhe'll never repent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:34.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A hand-me-down from\nour neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:40.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said your bike was\nlost over there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a bit rusted, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:46.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I'm really grateful.\NThank you, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:55.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, aren't you going to school?\NYou'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:56.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's gonna get dirty as soon\nas you take it back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not bad when Inuyasha\ncarries me on his back,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can really use this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's sparkling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:27.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:27.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:28.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:32.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inu....yasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you come to play again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:48.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Kagome, why'd you leave\nwithout asking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:52.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You broke it, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:58.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:00.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:02.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's bent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:05.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, you polished it until\nit was so shiny, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just do this and it'll go {\i1}back....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I just have to fix it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:21.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:23.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}okay....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you're upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:27.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}okay....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:28.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Good morning!\N- Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:49.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Geez, what's he doing here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he seems upset\nabout something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:54.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:55.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:57.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yuka! Eri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Did something happen\nwith that boyfriend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How come they're always\nso sharp?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:12.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:13.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:20.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So your delinquent boyfriend\nis two-timing you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, sort {\i1}of....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are circumstances\nthat can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:27.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So he's cheating on you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because he can't choose\nbetween you and the other woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:35.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Choose me or the other woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that Inuyasha\nhas feelings for Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:42.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was the one who decided\nto stay by him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:50.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought it was okay\nbecause I like Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay if he can't make\nup his mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but it's the pits if he's decided\nwho's first and who's second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? First and second?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean who he likes better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:07.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His first love or Kagome.\NWho does he like more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First or {\i1}second....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:17.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'm probably\n{\i1}second....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,being second isn't\nnecessarily a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Second stock is good\nfor miso soup
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,as well as for stewed dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But fine restaurants always use\nfirst stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But {\i1}remember....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in baseball, the catcher is number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the control tower\ncalling the pitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:45.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there's the second actor\nin kabuki and he's always handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:51.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:55.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe you'd be better off\nnot seeing him, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's one way to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:02.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I can't help it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:05.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,if he follows me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even today, from so early\nin the {\i1}morning....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:08.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's at your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:11.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:16.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's delinquent boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here. Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can it be fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that she got this from\nsomewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:42.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to replace the one that\ngot broken over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:45.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, our neighbor\ngave it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:48.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:49.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For breaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you're going to fix it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:05.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Somethin' like {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you {\i1}just....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit! Why doesn't it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:26.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:28.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leggo of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leggo, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:33.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't listen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:34.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:35.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:41.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way can one or two {\i1}rings....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:44.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:55.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of boy he is...\nthis selfish, two-timing ruffian boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't think they'd really\ncome along.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just awhile earlier, they were\ntelling me not to see him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:09.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,L-Look, we're all busy with exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no time {\i1}for....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:15.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:19.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, we have to scold him\nfor hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please don't! If you do that,\nhe'll have a fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have a fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's sounding more and\nmore unlikable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'd better put him\nin his place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let them meet Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a half-demon and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let his identity\nbe revealed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is all Inuyasha's fault!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coming around uninvited!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome seems troubled again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe you said too much, Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? It's my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe we shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:51.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of person he is,\NKagome likes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And to root her {\i1}on....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is what friends would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:13:59.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:01.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:06.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NWe're on your side, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:07.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how violent\nhe {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how two-timing\nhe {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}U-Umm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:23.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaa...! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An iron {\i1}cart....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:29.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks worse than\nit did this morni-!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I don't fix it,\NKagome {\i1}will....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you just\npay her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:42.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:46.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't this the Adamantite stone\nthat you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is called a diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:55.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With one of these, you can\nbuy lots and lots of bicycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll make oodles of 'em\nwith my Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Adamant Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strange....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Adamantite spears are\nsupposed to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:33.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, don't break anything more\nthan you already have!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! What a bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then how's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:41.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:46.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lemme at it until\nthey come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:49.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grandpa....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha wants to work\npart-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:59.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He'll work really hard for\nbreaking the bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I'm really expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:09.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh boy, I'm home already.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:11.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I going to do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's even more trouble to\nexplain to Inuyasha{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that he's not to come out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's back has "anguish"\nwritten all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When we meet her delinquent boyfriend,\nlet's be nice to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:26.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if he has a gangster haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:29.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And even if his pants are purple\nor pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:30.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An avant-garde sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:43.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Is that her boyfriend's name?\N- Hey, I know you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Maybe that's his gang name.\N- Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- He's a delinquent, right?\N- Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:53.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright! This one goes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And, next is this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Part-timer, that box goes\nover there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:05.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I think Kagome is calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You probably imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:16.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, bring that jar\nover here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:22.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That jar has a storied history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be very {\i1}careful....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:35.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh! The jar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:36.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:36.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's in the shed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:40.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:41.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa, where's Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He....ran{\i0} away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:54.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He breaks everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:03.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I think he already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were looking forward\nto it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he comes around\nquite often, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Well, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh well, I think\nit worked out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:21.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, he's so weird.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, come and\nget the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:25.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too bad.\NI wanted to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:40.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We came all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:45.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been upset\nsince this morn-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You wouldn't happen to {\i1}be....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Say....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could {\i1}he....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You {\i1}guys....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Pekopon who ran amok\nat the school play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:08.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! The one who had a run-in\nwith Hojo during the cultural festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was Kagome's boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:13.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did Kagome ask you\nto do that back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err....yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:20.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is Inuyasha...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're going to find out\nthat he's a half-demon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When did you start seeing Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:35.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}kimono....{\i0} Do you work\nat the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your eyes are an unusual color.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you bleach your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was born with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's such an unusual color.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:45.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:48.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:51.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}- They're carrying on a conversation.{\i0}\N- It's so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, is he half?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hafu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:58.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:00.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a half-demon, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:07.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh....he's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm jealous, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:13.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- You lived overseas?\N- When'd you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:30.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be seeing you.\N'Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:34.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, he's not as bad\nas you made him out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:38.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought he'd look and dress\nlike a street gang member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He is a bit different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not at all like I had imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:46.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You two get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now the problem is Hojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, he doesn't know about\nthe boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Were they praising Inuyasha?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:02.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right! They think he's cool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't need it, do you?\NThat thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:17.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:19.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That iron cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll carry you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:27.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you, Grandpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:36.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha said he can create\ndiamonds with Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:38.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you make him\nrepay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One, {\i1}two....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm missing the third.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:46.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't believe me, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}missing....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll apologize to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:54.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:57.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It just....doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:47.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A young girl who is chosen\nto be the bride of a demon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:49.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,makes a shocking confession!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:52.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that I was\nbetrothed to Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:53.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:55.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll forgive the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:58.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so come and live with me\nat the bottom of the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:00.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango! I can explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:01.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:04.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess this wasn't meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:08.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Miroku's Past Mistake"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:12.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, can't you trust me at all?
